## 1. C ch hot ng

Ta xt mt v d n gin nh sau:

```tsx
import { Button, Checkbox, Form, Input } from 'antd';

const onFinish = (values) => {
  console.log('Success:', values);
};

const App = () => (
  <Form onFinish={onFinish}>
    <Form.Item name='username'>
      <Input />
    </Form.Item>

    <Button type='primary' htmlType='submit'>
      Submit
    </Button>
  </Form>
);
```

![Demo 1](https://res.cloudinary.com/hunghg255/image/upload/v1679199291/blog/Screenshot_2023-03-19_at_11.14.37_lp70zv.png)

Nh ta thy khi t component `Input` trong `Form.Item` vi `name` l `username` th khi submit s nhn c mt object vi key l `username` v value l gi tr ca input.

Vy c phi c t `Input` bn trong `Form.Item` l ta s ly c value ca Input khi submit khng?
Mnh s custom xu l thm ci label hoc cn tu bin input thm prefix hoc suffix icon,...

```tsx
<Form.Item name='username'>
  <Row>
    <label>Username</label>
    <Input />
  </Row>
</Form.Item>
```

![Demo 2](https://res.cloudinary.com/hunghg255/image/upload/v1679200848/blog/Screenshot_2023-03-19_at_11.40.41_onm9lw.png)

Vn cho mnh cng kt qu. nu ta mun dng nhiu ni th phi copy sang nhiu ch khc nhau. vy mnh s tch thnh mt component  sau c th ti s dng

```tsx
const CustomInput = () => {
  return (
    <Row>
      <label>Username</label>
      <Input />
    </Row>
  );
};

<Form.Item name='username'>
  <CustomInput />
</Form.Item>;
```

![Demo 3](https://res.cloudinary.com/hunghg255/image/upload/v1679200637/blog/Screenshot_2023-03-19_at_11.37.10_ixmjsf.png)

Mnh kim tra li kt qu xem sao. Ops kt qu khng nh ta mong i. Khi tch thnh component  c th ti s dng th khng cn ly c value ca `input` na. Vy chuyn g  xy ra m khi t trong `Form.Item` th c kt qu v mnh mun tch ra c th ti s dng li khng hot ng.

Mnh s kim tra `props` ca `CustomInput` xem c g bt thng khng nh =)))

![props](https://res.cloudinary.com/hunghg255/image/upload/v1679201545/blog/Screenshot_2023-03-19_at_11.52.18_byltfn.png)

:::note
Nh ta thy `props` ca `CustomInput` l mt object cha `id`, `value`, `onChange`. Tc l khi ta t Input ngay bn trong `Form.Item` th n t ng pass props  vo cho `Input` v vy ta s ly c value ca Input.

Khi mnh tch ra thnh mt component  ti s dng th `value` v `onChange` s khng c pass vo Input na nn ta s khng ly c value ca Input
:::

Ok. vy mnh s th fix bng cch pass `value` v `onChange` vo Input xem sao.

![fix](https://res.cloudinary.com/hunghg255/image/upload/v1679202119/blog/Screenshot_2023-03-19_at_12.01.50_lk5yyg.png)

Oh. Hihi kt qu nh mong i

:::note
Kt lun: Khi ta mun truyn value t component bt k ln `Form.Item` ta ch cn dng hm `onChange` t `Form.Item` ci m c truyn xung props khi t component trong `Form.Item`
:::

## 2. C ch hot ng `dependencies`, `shouldUpdate` v `useWatch`

### a. Dependencies

Mnh c mt v d n gin nh sau: c 3 select gm tnh, huyn, x.
Yu cu: Khi chn tnh th s ti danh sch huyn, khi chn huyn th s ti danh sch x.

S c nhiu cch x l bi ton ny. nh mt s anh em s x l bng cch dng state lu li gi tr tnh, huyn, x. c thay i v state th lng nghe trong `useEffect`  ti list huyn, x. Cch ny s nh hng n performance nu m form c nhiu field.

 y mnh s chn cch gii quyt bng cch dng `dependencies`

u tin mnh s to custom select tnh, huyn, x:

Bnh thng data s c ly t API nhng trong v d ny mnh s ti v sn lun.

```tsx
// Ly data cc tnh t API
const SelectProvince = (props) => {
  const { value, onChange } = props;

  return (
    <Select
      placeholder='Chn Tnh'
      value={value}
      onChange={onChange}
      options={provinces.map((provinceItem) => {
        return {
          label: provinceItem.name_with_type,
          value: provinceItem.code,
        };
      })}
    />
