### c. useWatch

`useWatch` l mt hook c cung cp bi form antd, dng  lng nghe nhng field m c thay i

Mnh s update li 2 component select ca mnh nh sau: Thay v truyn t props xung th mnh dng `useWatch`  ly data mi nht khi c thay i

```tsx
const SelectDistrict = (props) => {
  const { value, onChange } = props;
  const province = Form.useWatch(['province']);

  ...
};
```

```tsx
